data.description: Welcome home to this better than new two story, stone, colonial located in the Lambert Estates development in Forks Twp -  this 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home has 9 foot ceilings on the first floor - family room with vaulted ceiling - hardwood floors - stone gas fireplace and dual staircase - bright and sunny eat-in kitchen with granite counter tops - tumbled stone backsplash - center island - formal living room with hardwood floors - dining room with hardwood floors and tray ceiling - 1st floor office with hardwood floors - the 2nd floor has a HUGE primary bedroom with a tray ceiling - extra sitting area and large attached bath - three additional generously sized bedrooms - fully finished lower level with storage and walkout - The large 1/2 acre+ lot is fenced and has a paver patio and maintenance free deck - List of updates include: replacement windows, upgraded gas line, newer HVAC, gas water heater (2019), roof (2022), solar panels (owned with warranty), garage doors, storage shed, security system - the list goes on!  Conveniently located close to major hwy US-22 for easy commute, Riverview Country Club, Forks Community Park, scenic Delaware River, Crayola Experience, shops, restaurants & so much more! Schedule your private showing today to see for yourself.
